# Class: obo:COB_0000082 (planned process)

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 obo:COB_0000082 "A process that is initiated by an agent who intends to carry out a plan to achieve an objective through one or more actions as described in a plan specification."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label obo:COB_0000082 "planned process"@en)
SubClassOf(obo:COB_0000082 obo:BFO_0000015)
DisjointClasses(obo:COB_0000082 co:PMD_0025009)

