AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition co:PMD_0000101 "A textual entity that denotes a workflow function via import resolution rules"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(co:PMD_0001032 co:PMD_0000101 <https://github.com/materialdigital/core-ontology/issues/280>)
SubClassOf(co:PMD_0000101 obo:IAO_0000300)
