AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition co:PMD_0000119 "A structural composite designed as a lightweight beam or panel consisting of two stiff and strong outer face sheets separated by a lightweight core layer with a low modulus of elasticity"@en)
SubClassOf(co:PMD_0000119 co:PMD_0000117)
