# Class: co:PMD_0000122 (laminate ply role)

AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label co:PMD_0000122 "laminate ply role"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(skos:definition co:PMD_0000122 "a single two-dimensional sheet that provides a specific high-strength orientation within a multi-layered stack"@en)
SubClassOf(co:PMD_0000122 obo:BFO_0000023)

